{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1677-08_007", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Madrigal sur l’Amour & le Respect]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Nouveau Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", août 1677 (tome VI), p. 7-9."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Voicy un autre Madrigal que nous devons encor à l’Amour."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "MADRIGAL."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Respect & l’Amour pleins de glace & de flame,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Se font la guerre dans mon ame,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " Et ne se veulent point ceder :"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais, ô Beauté charmante & rare,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " Si je ne puis les accorder,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " Permettez que je les separe."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Un Amour sans respect fait toûjours de grandes entreprises ; c’est un Enfant perdu qui va bien viste, & qu’il est bien difficile d’arrester. Il pousse ses affaires plus loin qu’on ne croit dés qu’on luy a laissé faire le premier pas ; & qui veut empescher ses progrés, ne luy doit d’abord rien pardonner. Je sçay, Madame, que c’est vostre sentiment, & que vous estes ennemie declarée de ces Amans sans respect dont la trop grande hardiesse declare toûjours la guerre à la pudeur."}]}]}